<script async>
const SCRIPTCORK_UNQORK_ROOT_CLASS = ".unqorkio-form";

const _$getScope = () => {
  return angular.element(SCRIPTCORK_UNQORK_ROOT_CLASS).scope();
};

const _$getForm = () => {
  let form = _$getScope().form;
  return form ?? null;
};

const _$getComponents = () => {
  let form = _$getForm();
  if (form.components) {
    return form.components;
  }

  return null;
};

const _$getComponent = (componentName) => {
  let components = _$getComponents();
  if (!components) return;

  if (Array.isArray(components)) {
    return components.find((component) => component.key === componentName);
  }

  return null;
};

const trigger = (componentName) => {
  if (!componentName) return;
  let component = _$getComponent(componentName);

  if (typeof component.execute === "function") {
